&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-style: italic;"&gt;As we already know, the First Lady’s documentary didn’t go over very well. If anything, it just reinforced the perception of her as someone who is cold and out of touch with the real world. Now, is putting her next to a robot the only way to make her seem more human? It seems that’s the new idea from her team of advisors...&lt;/p&gt;
